1. Determine the maximum torque [`T_{0_{max}}`] applied at section [`C`]?
2. Determine [`T_{0_{max}}`] if the maximum angle of twist is [`[$maxangle]^{\circ}`]. 


[`T_{0_{max_1}}=`] [_____]{"$t1"} [`Nm`]  
